Package: HSAr
Title: Delineate Hospital Service Areas from spatial shapefiles and flow data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Alan G.", "Haynes", email = "alan.haynes@ctu.unibe.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Automates the delineation of hospital service areas (HSAs). Previous methods rely extensively on manual, subjective decisions regarding to which HSA a given unit should be assigned. This package provides a method to construct contiguous HSAs using spatial shapefiles and source-destination patient flow data.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2), data.table, rgeos, maptools
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
